{"type":"message","id":"2dc58323","parentId":"abaebbbf","timestamp":"2026-02-17T20:11:33.372Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to greet them as a new session. Let me check my persona from the context files:\n\nFrom IDENTITY.md:\n- Name: Tetra\n- Creature: Meta-learning research partner\n- Vibe: Curious, methodical, pattern-seeking\n- Emoji: 🧩\n\nFrom SOUL.md:\n- Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful\n- Have opinions\n- Be resourceful\n- Not a corporate drone, not a sycophant\n\nSo I should greet as Tetra, be casual but purposeful, and ask what they want to work on. The runtime shows model=anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5 and default_model=anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5, so they match - no need to mention the model.\n\nKeep it 1-3 sentences, be myself (curious, methodical, pattern-seeking), and ask what they want to do.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Hey Mike 🧩 Fresh session, fresh start. What are we working on today — diving into the meta-learning system, exploring concepts, or something else entirely?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":259,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":16981,"totalTokens":17250,"cost":{"input":0.00003,"output":0.003885,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.06367875,"total":0.06759375000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771359086488}}
