{"type":"message","id":"3b7bba0d","parentId":"0235b733","timestamp":"2026-02-17T20:30:59.482Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent just a \"-\" which could mean:\n1. They're testing the system\n2. The report is empty/cancelled\n3. There's a transmission issue\n4. They're waiting for something\n\nGiven the context of Throng4 testing and the repeated messages, this might be part of the system testing the bridge or observation flow. I should acknowledge but not over-interpret.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Got it — Episode 9 report is empty or cancelled.\n\nLet me know when you have data to analyze, or if you want to discuss the training approach differently!"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":129,"cacheRead":39705,"cacheWrite":67,"totalTokens":39911,"cost":{"input":0.00003,"output":0.001935,"cacheRead":0.0119115,"cacheWrite":0.00025125,"total":0.01412775}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771360252081}}
